♪ Your mama's on crack rock ♪

1028
00:58:16.493 --> 00:58:18.036
♪ Not my mama ♪

1029
00:58:18.119 --> 00:58:20.330
♪ Your mama's on crack rock ♪

1030
00:58:20.413 --> 00:58:21.873
♪ You guys lyin' ♪

1031
00:58:21.956 --> 00:58:24.876
[Hart] The people who were smoking crack
were vilified...

1032
